    Class Description
    Demo
    This class sets up the DataBase for the class demo according to the specifications of the professor.
    Info
    Stores the information: Instructions and AboutUs
    PlayerStatistics

    User
    This class is the abstraction of a User containing essential properties like the a username, password and the game history.

    Compares the Users in a LinkedList of Users according to the User's total wins
    UserAuth
    This class provides login credential services.
    UserDataBase
    This class is the abstraction for a database containing User objects.
    UserDataBase.UserDataBaseWriter
    This class is the abstraction of the database I/O.
